description:
The Sixth Day Before Christmas: Episode Four is narrated by Mary’s mother. She tells of the care she and her husband took to keep Mary from having any real or perceived questionable reputation. She is thrilled that Mary is betrothed to a Godly man named Joseph. Mary's mother tells of raising her daughter in the most proper manner, and her thankfulness that Joseph and Mary will soon be married. Eyewitness Bible Series is pleased to present the Christmas Series. This series is a collection of 10 new episodes designed to be watched on the three Sundays prior to Christmas week, plus the seven days of Christmas week, ending on Christmas Day. Scripture: Luke 1:26-28
